elements.2211.03282_756ded55e6bce83319f9df632b431: Recent advances in deep learning have led to the development of models approaching human level of accuracy
elements.2211.03282_dbbc1a6a3713112e6546dd0ec612d: However, healthcare remains an area lacking in widespread adoption
elements.2211.03282_ca5b739414fd135e91ccde617462f: The safety-critical nature of healthcare results in a natural reticence to put these black-box deep learning models into practice
elements.2211.03282_60fb87646a0edcc63a7fa0ba84781: In this paper, we explore interpretable methods for a clinical decision support system, sleep staging, based on physiological signals such as EEG, EOG, and EMG
elements.2211.03282_e4e6554d3e9802e74245365ca1169: A recent work has shown sleep staging using simple models and an exhaustive set of features can perform nearly as well as deep learning approaches but only for certain datasets
elements.2211.03282_05d5261da0cec7a451ebc1e1e6186: Moreover, the utility of these features from a clinical standpoint is unclear
elements.2211.03282_d1b359199943d39483f4fe262a78e: On the other hand, the proposed framework,
elements.2211.03282_6174756858762f8347f35c34c5294: shows that by representing deep learning embeddings using normalized features, great performance can be obtained across different datasets.
elements.2211.03282_a685e731c28e6bc9aa929fb0eb69e: better than the exhaustive feature-based approach and 1.5
elements.2211.03282_d2c7a18a5214853ae1a9647c37b9f: better than other representation learning approaches
elements.2211.03282_63b0a20729b3e2276e33bb4ba9a15: An empirical comparison between the utility of the interpretations of these models highlights the improved alignment with clinical expectations when performance is traded-off slightly.
elements.2211.03282_b88e8a5fbcc14a10bbdae6821cf25: There has been a steady accumulation of digital records of patient health data due to the increasingly widespread adoption of electronic health records
elements.2211.03282_775f645c7165386292514bb0964da: Breakthroughs in deep learning have leveraged this influx of clinical data to create increasingly complex and capable systems
elements.2211.03282_dbb86abb96cafad0ca6a002e284d7: However, the lack of interpretability and explainability of deep learning models prevents most of them from being used in practice because clinicians need to understand the explanation behind each classification to avoid noise and bias
elements.2211.03282_b1af40cc95307b93b65a1271c2489: Although challenging to design due to the manual effort required, linear models paired with a robust set of features can provide a degree of interpretability
elements.2211.03282_98a85e0c7901e4b1faae20bac0c35: However, linear models paired with complex features may result in models whose interpretation does not have clinical relevance
elements.2211.03282_20731604632b5e65da4d3b8499547: In this paper, using sleep staging as a case study, we take a deeper dive into the trade-off between clinical relevance of explanations and performance, and propose a model attempting to tackle this issue
elements.2211.03282_e244bba89dda77ca22b0bc7b06458: Around 70 million US adults are affected by sleep disorders
elements.2211.03282_b9a78e47d8848f39d368632d4b0aa: such as insomnia, narcolepsy, or sleep apnea
elements.2211.03282_208dd252d72fa5187c992f2e485f2: The most crucial step for the diagnosis of sleep disorders is sleep staging
elements.2211.03282_68a6a6ade171e3a803093c6fe5234: The gold standard for sleep staging remains manual annotation of Polysomnogram (PSG) by clinicians
elements.2211.03282_cca2001e278c33b90701f2965a4ac: During this process, clinicians inspect the PSG signals from multiple channels, and annotate each 30s segment with one of five sleep stages, i.e. wake, rapid eye movement (REM), and the non-REM stages N1, N2, and N3, by following guidelines stated in the American Academy of Sleep Medicine (AASM) Manual for the Scoring of Sleep and Associated Events
elements.2211.03282_2c7060b0c77eae396531e2a2a7e57: This manual annotation scheme is time-consuming and expensive because a clinician needs several hours to annotate a patientâs recordings from a single night
elements.2211.03282_cb758e653492c5249373f3702dbe6: There has been considerable research in automating sleep staging to overcome this
elements.2211.03282_5e175dd6be61bc1183e7bdebc0b44: These approaches have mostly remained in the realm of deep learning that lack interpretability
elements.2211.03282_d90e545e2d8929341fb2f56a0a50e: On the other hand, the AASM sleep scoring manual guidelines
elements.2211.03282_d7eefc7b612cf4d583727a500ff74: , are interpretable for clinicians without providing the clear definitions needed to design a robust computational model
elements.2211.03282_ac0647461a75c38ca81e67b75c8d3: A recent study proposed a feature-based linear model
elements.2211.03282_97ae035f57d20cc71e308de3e6f89: that performed as well as deep neural network models
elements.2211.03282_f9bffd034bfb05755562126d36ee9: However, the features used in this study were not designed considering clinical guidelines
elements.2211.03282_fdf5d5130c7e758131c45d3c0a877: In order to generate clinically relevant explanations, we propose
elements.2211.03282_5a7f3923b799c2ecd10230cc864bc: , a representation learning framework that projects deep neural network embeddings into an interpretable normalized feature space
elements.2211.03282_5f86d7afbd8d6881223f11cb4d86f: Thus, by choosing an appropriate feature space,
elements.2211.03282_7a7a4b011d6daa856ad9d665ce732: can unite clinically relevant explanations with the high accuracy of a deep learning model.
